UI vesamenu.c32
PROMPT 0
TIMEOUT 100
ONTIMEOUT arch-live

MENU TABMSG Press ENTER to boot or TAB to edit a menu entry
MENU AUTOBOOT BIOS default device boot in # second{,s}...
MENU BACKGROUND splash.png
MENU WIDTH 78
MENU MARGIN 4
MENU ROWS 12
MENU VSHIFT 2
MENU TIMEOUTROW 13
MENU TABMSGROW 2
MENU CMDLINEROW 16
MENU HELPMSGROW 20
MENU HELPMSGENDROW 34

MENU COLOR title         * #FF5255FF *
MENU COLOR border        * #00000000 #00000000 none
MENU COLOR sel           * #ffffffff #FF5255FF *

LABEL arch-live
MENU LABEL @@BOOT_TITLE@@ (@@ARCH@@) BIOS
LINUX /boot/@@KERNEL_FILE@@
APPEND initrd=/boot/@@INITRAMFS_FILE@@ archisobasedir=arch archisosearchuuid=@@ARCHISO_UUID@@ @@BOOT_CMDLINE@@

LABEL arch-rescue
MENU LABEL Rescue Mode (Command Line)
LINUX /boot/@@KERNEL_FILE@@
APPEND initrd=/boot/@@INITRAMFS_FILE@@ archisobasedir=arch archisosearchuuid=@@ARCHISO_UUID@@ nomodeset vga=normal @@BOOT_CMDLINE@@

LABEL reboot
MENU LABEL ^Reboot
COM32 reboot.c32

LABEL poweroff
MENU LABEL ^Power Off
COM32 poweroff.c32